// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0314 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 89365d54-49dc-5c12-b468-f8b32b5669e5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
